        "id": 5620
      },
      "writtenOn": "2017-02-15T16:29:06Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "You are correct, that number is essentially unbound and could be all unique digests in the current tile. \nCurrently that is about 30k. The GetRefDiffs below potentially triggers O(nDigests^2) go-routines further down the stack. \nMost of those will be cached, but we have seen 650k active go-routines in Gold. The cores were maxed out and the system got slower, but remained responsive at all times and eventually the go-routine count got down ~80 again.",
      "parentUuid": "6864d69c_2eb82a59",
